HI I’M ALEX FARNHAM AND THIS IS ANIMALIST
NEWS- FUN FACTS!

WE’VE ALL HAD A BAD KISS IN OUR LIFETIME,
BUT FEMALE WHITE FRONTED PARROTS HAVE THEM

ALL THE TIME!
NATIVE TO CENTRAL AMERICA, THESE PARROTS ARE

ONE OF THE ONLY ANIMALS BESIDES HUMANS AND
PRIMATES THAT SHOW AFFECTION THROUGH MOUTH

TO MOUTH KISSING
HOW ADORABLE!

WHAT’S NOT ADORABLE IS THE FACT THAT MALE
PARROTS BECOME SO AROUSED BY MAKING OUT THAT

THEY VOMIT INTO THE FEMALE’S MOUTH!
EW!

BUT THEY DON’T SEE IT THIS WAY, FEMALES
GENERALLY SWALLOW THE VOMIT AND SEE IT AS

A SIGN OF LOVE. AWWWEE
I GUESS MALES FEEL THE NEED TO SHARE THEIR

LUNCH AS WELL AS PARENTING SKILLS.
AFTER THE DIRTY PARROT DEED IS DONE, FEMALES

LAY THREE TO FOUR EGGS THAT THEY BOTH TAKE
CARE OF FOR ABOUT TEN WEEKS.

BANANA SLUGS, LIKE MOST SLUGS, ARE HERMAPHRODITES
AND ENGAGE EACH OTHER BY FIGHTING WITH THEIR

PENISES IN ORDER TO FERTILIZE THE OTHER SLUG.
THE PART THAT MAKES BANANA SLUGS DIFFERENT

IS THAT THEIR PENIS IS HUGE!
THE AVERAGE SIZE OF A BANANA SLUG PENIS IS

SEVEN INCHES, WHICH IS PRETTY ADMIRABLE CONSIDERING
THEIR ENTIRE BODY LENGTH IS ONLY SIX TO EIGHT

INCHES LONG!
IN THE BANANA SLUGS CASE, SIZE DOES MATTER,

SO IT’S IMPORTANT TO FIND A MATE THAT IS
AROUND THE SAME SIZE.

BECAUSE IF IT’S PENIS GETS STUCK IN A SMALLER
SLUG THE OTHER SLUG WILL BITE IT OFF!

OH AND I’M SURE WE’VE ALL HEARD SOMEONE
SAY “I FEEL LIKE WE’RE THE SAME PERSON!”

AND FOR THE ANGLER FISH, THAT STATEMENT IS
ALL TOO TRUE.

HAVE YOU EVER MET A MALE ANGLER FISH?
CHANCES ARE NO.

MALES ARE BORN WITHOUT A DIGESTIVE SYSTEM,
SO THEY HAVE TO FIND A MATE FAST.

ONCE THE MALE FINDS A FEMALE, HE BITES HER
AND RELEASES AN ENZYME THAT DIGESTS HIS SKIN.

THE MALE IS ABSORBED INTO THE FEMALE, BUT
LEAVES HIS SPERM BEHIND WHICH SHE RELEASES

WHEN READY TO MATE.
HOW ROMANTIC!
WELL THAT’S ALL FOR TODAY’S EPISODE….
